    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and runs smoothly, offering a dependable and comfortable driving experience for its next owner. While the exterior and interior are clean and well-kept, you may find some minor cosmetic wear consistent with regular use, such as small stone chips or light interior scuffs. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that is ready for many more miles on the road.",
      "price": 35500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly immaculate, showroom condition. This masterpiece has been meticulously preserved, boasting a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that retains its original luster. Every component reflects a rigorous standard of care, ensuring an unrivaled driving experience that feels indistinguishable from new. For the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than the absolute best, this vehicle represents the gold standard of pre-owned excellence.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019ve been a total car nut my whole life, and let me tell you, finding a gem like this is getting harder every day. This beauty has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014always tucked away in the garage and pampered with the best care possible. It drives absolutely like a dream, smooth and responsive, just like the day it was born. You might find a tiny, tiny mark if you really go looking for it, but honestly, it\u2019s about as close to showroom perfect as you can get. I\u2019m really looking for someone who will love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously curated example for the discerning driver. This chassis exhibits exceptional torsional rigidity, paired with a powertrain that has been maintained to a rigorous standard. We\u2019ve addressed the common failure points with preventative upgrades: the VANOS system has been completely overhauled with bespoke seals, and the rod bearings were replaced with treated shells for peace of mind at high RPMs. The induction note is sharpened via a carbon-fiber intake, providing a linear power delivery through the entire rev range. Suspension geometry is dialed in with adjustable coilovers, ensuring zero-lash steering response and flat cornering. The paintwork has undergone a multi-stage correction and is sealed with a ceramic coating, preserving the factory luster. This isn\u2019t just a car; it\u2019s a high-performance instrument that has been over-engineered for reliability. Comprehensive service history included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Showroom quality. Zero flaws. Like new. Lowest price for this condition. Act fast.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time machine finished in a deep, lustrous Midnight Azure that seems to swallow the moonlight. Slide into the cockpit and you\u2019re greeted by the rich, heady aroma of hand-stitched saddle leather, preserved as if the decades never passed. When the engine awakens, it doesn\u2019t just start; it clears its throat with a velvet growl that promises endless coastal drives and the envious stares of every passerby. Every curve of its polished chrome tells a story of elegance and a life well-lived. To own this masterpiece is to own a piece of automotive poetry, a pristine relic of an era where style was the only currency that mattered.",
      "price": 46800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive excellence with this showroom-quality masterpiece. Meticulously preserved and presenting in absolute mint condition, this vehicle offers an uncompromising driving experience. From its flawless exterior finish to the factory-fresh interior, every detail reflects a standard of care rarely seen on the market. This is an investment-grade acquisition for the discerning driver who demands nothing less than perfection. Fully inspected and ready for immediate delivery.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy the ride of their life. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014always garage-kept, pampered with the best wax, and driven only on the sunniest weekends. It truly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! There might be a tiny, barely-there speck from a pebble on the highway, but you\u2019d honestly have to squint to find it. This is a rare find in such incredible shape, and I\u2019m looking for a buyer who will cherish it as much as I have. Come by, let's grab a coffee, and I'll show you why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E92 M3 that redefines the 'mint' standard. This S65 power plant has been fastidiously maintained with documented rod bearing replacement using VAC coated bearings and ARP bolts to eliminate the factory's inherent clearance issues. The high-pressure VANOS system has been fully overhauled with upgraded seals, ensuring razor-sharp variable valve timing across the entire 8,400 RPM sweep. The DCT transmission has been flashed with the GTS software for aggressive, zero-latency shifts, while the chassis sits on a perfectly corner-balanced Ohlins Road & Track suspension setup. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, protected by a multi-stage ceramic coating. This isn't just a car; it's a mechanically optimized masterpiece with zero deferred maintenance and a subframe that's been reinforced for structural rigidity. If you understand the engineering behind the last naturally aspirated V8 M-car, you know this build is beyond reproach.",
      "price": 49250.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 11
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_8",
